  "remarks": "\nYekaterina Sergeyevna VINOKUROVA is closely associated with Sergei Viktorovich LAVROV, the Foreign Minister of Russia who is her father. Sergei Viktorovich LAVROV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
